    <automated>DOTNET_ROLL_FORWARD=LatestMajor DOTNET_ROLL_FORWARD_TO_PRERELEASE=1 arch -arm64 dotnet build -c Release ThermoRawFileParser/ThermoRawFileParser.csproj && arch -arm64 dotnet ThermoRawFileParser/bin/Release/net8.0/ThermoRawFileParser.dll --help 2>&1 | grep -i -E "no-numpress|lossless"</automated>
  </verify>
  <done>numpress is ON by default; --no-numpress/--lossless -> delta chunks; --point -> v1 point; lossy-m/z warning fires only in numpress mode; help documents all three. (NP-03)</done>
